OL,3,CEFL investigates Middlesbrough
OL,4,Ccomplaint over alleged filming by
OL,5,CSouthampton
OL,7,FThe English Football League has
OL,8,Freceived a complaint from
OL,9,FMiddlesbrough following allegations of
OL,10,Funauthorised filming by someone
OL,11,Fassociated with Southampton during a
OL,12,Ftraining session.
OL,14,FAhead of the two teams' Championship
OL,15,Fplay-off semi-final first leg this
OL,16,Fweekend, reports on Thursday claimed
OL,17,Fthat an "individual identified to be
OL,18,Fassociated with Southampton" had
OL,19,Fallegedly been filming Boro training
OL,20,Fand ` as a result ` the EFL has
OL,21,Fwritten to Southampton regarding this.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
