OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1778217986
OL,3,CEFL investigates Middlesbrough
OL,4,Ccomplaint over alleged filming by
OL,5,CSouthampton
OL,7,FBoth teams are set to meet at the
OL,8,FRiverside Stadium on Saturday, with
OL,9,Fthe second leg of their semi-final set
OL,10,Fto take place at St Mary's next
OL,11,FTuesday night.
OL,13,FThe EFL confirmed that the alleged
OL,14,Fincident was being considered as
OL,15,F"potential misconduct" under their
OL,16,Fregulations.
