PN,42103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1778217986
OL,3,CEFL investigates Middlesbrough
OL,4,Ccomplaint over alleged filming by
OL,5,CSouthampton
OL,7,FAn EFL spokesperson said: "The EFL has
OL,8,Fwritten to Southampton requesting
OL,9,Ftheir observations following a
OL,10,Fcomplaint from Middlesbrough relating
OL,11,Fto alleged unauthorised filming ahead
OL,12,Fof the two clubs meeting in Saturday's
OL,13,FChampionship play-off semi-final first
OL,14,Fleg.
OL,16,F"The alleged incident is said to have
OL,17,Ftaken place on Middlesbrough's private
OL,18,Fproperty by an individual identified
OL,19,Fto be associated with Southampton.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
