PN,42104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1778217986
OL,3,CEFL investigates Middlesbrough
OL,4,Ccomplaint over alleged filming by
OL,5,CSouthampton
OL,7,F"The League is treating this matter as
OL,8,Fpotential misconduct under EFL
OL,9,FRegulations and will be making no
OL,10,Ffurther comment at this time."
OL,12,FSouthampton reached the play-offs with
OL,13,Fa fourth-placed finish in the
OL,14,FChampionship and Boro finished one
OL,15,Fspot below them on goal difference
OL,16,Fafter both sides secured 80 points.
OL,18,FBoth Southampton and Middlesbrough
OL,19,Fhave been contacted for comment.
